			<pb n="1"/>
				<p><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Enclosed I forward<lb/> you by friend <persName>G. Kursheedt Esq.</persName> the balance of our account<lb/> say Thirty Seven Dollars.  I hope you will pardon me<lb/> for my neglect in not sending it before&#44; but rest assured<lb/> that <sic>unforseen</sic> circumstances&#44; which <persName>Mr K</persName> can explain to you<lb/> were the cause.  Hoping this will meet you in the best<lb/> enjoyment of health.  I remain</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Respectfully yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">B. da Silva</persName></p>
				<p><placeName>New Orleans</placeName> <date>May 25<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1854</date>.</p>
